Title: Soldier Borne Mission Command (SBMC)                                                                                                  76.341          308.038     337.958
Description: Soldier Borne Mission Command (SBMC) provides Soldiers and Squads a single platform for increased lethality,
mobility, and situational awareness to achieve overmatch against our current and future adversaries. IVAS transitioned to an
expanded capability called SBMC which builds lessons learned from Integrated Visual Augmentation System (IVAS) and the
Enhanced Night Vision Goggle - Binocular (ENVG-B) by delivering a modular, fused digital awareness system that enhances
lethality, mobility, and situational awareness for dismounted Soldiers. SBMC also addresses operational priorities that include
network improvements, accelerated Human Machine Interface (HMI) and robotic-enabled maneuver though extensibility and a
Company and below Squad architecture.



