D. Acquisition Strategy
The FALCONS Abbreviated Capability Development Document (A-CDD) was approved 23 March 2023. The program was approved by the AAE on 17 November 2023
to proceed with a Middle-Tier Acquisition-Rapid Prototyping (MTA-RP) approach using an Other Transaction Agreement (OTA). FALCONS awarded a competitive OTA
to three vendors in 4QFY2025 to finalize a Government performance specification. The program plans to develop the required program entrance documentation to
initiate the MTA-RP effort in FY 2026.




