FY 2027 Plans:
Conduct flight test 3, begin engineering development test (EDT) flight testing, complete subsystem qualification testing, develop
a pilot production line, conduct a seeker critical design review (CDR), award the EOC-2 production contract (IDIQ delivery order),
and prepare for EDT-1 and system CDR.
FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
The FY 2027 funding increase supports flight tests and continuing increment 2 development.
