 with a scalable and open systems architecture to mitigate evolving threats and integrates into the Missile Defense System through the Command and Control, Battle
 Management, and Communications system. This Program Element includes Missile Defense System threat discrimination improvements to enhance effectiveness
 against the evolving threat environment. The result will be a Missile Defense System architecture more capable of discriminating against and interpreting re-entry
