development and deployment of a layered Missile Defense System. This system is designed to defend the homeland from missile attacks of all ranges, in all phases of
flight. The LRDR's contribution provides persistent long-range midcourse discrimination, precision tracking and hit assessment, thereby enhancing the Missile Defense
