- Achieve OA.
- Complete Transition and Transfer to USSF.
- Continue Increment 6C/7 Ground Testing.
- Continue Increment 10 capability development.
- Continue providing Interim Contractor Support (Phase 3) and necessary forward engineering to support CSFS.
FY 2026 Plans:
- Complete Expanded Homeland Defense software upgrade.
- Deliver expanded Homeland Defense upgrade to the OCL.

