D. Acquisition Strategy
The acquisition strategy for MDA Consolidated Support consists of contract actions to industry for: a) Engineering and technical support; b) studies, analyses, and
evaluations; and c) management and professional services to MDA functional organizations and program offices. With a focus to achieve Small Business goals, MDA is
leveraging existing contracts and will competitively award new contracts to meet MDA's FYs 2020-2030 Advisory and Assistance Services support.




